chai","last_touched":1676780121,"title":"快速将 ChatGPT 接入飞书，作为私人工作助理或者企业员工助理","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/917278","created":1676766112,"deleted":0,"content":"### 项目地址： https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu\r\n\r\n### 项目描述：\r\n\r\n快速将 ChatGPT 接入飞书，作为私人工作助理或者企业员工助理\r\n\r\n（需要注意的是，目前接入的是 OpenAI 的 GPT3 模型，实现了长对话，效果类似 ChatGPT ，但不是 ChatGPT ，后续考虑接入 BingChat ，或者等 OpenAI 开放 ChatGPT API ）\r\n\r\n### 功能支持\r\n\r\n* 支持长对话，自动联系上下文\r\n* 支持私人对话\r\n* 支持群聊\r\n  * 支持 @ 机器人回复\r\n  * 也支持命令（`/chatgpt`）触发，格式：`/chatgpt 你的聊天内容`\r\n* [ WIP] 支持配置启动反向代理\r\n* [WIP] 支持二次开发，快速接入企业现有应用\r\n* [WIP] 支持 BingChat \r\n\r\n### 预览\r\n\r\n![]( https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu/raw/master/docs/assets/images/chatgpt.chat.group.png)\r\n\r\n![]( https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu/raw/master/docs/assets/images/chatgpt.chat.p2p.png)","content_rendered":"<h3>项目地址： <a href=\"https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu</a></h3>\n<h3>项目描述：</h3>\n<p>快速将 ChatGPT 接入飞书，作为私人工作助理或者企业员工助理</p>\n<p>（需要注意的是，目前接入的是 OpenAI 的 GPT3 模型，实现了长对话，效果类似 ChatGPT ，但不是 ChatGPT ，后续考虑接入 BingChat ，或者等 OpenAI 开放 ChatGPT API ）</p>\n<h3>功能支持</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>支持长对话，自动联系上下文</li>\n<li>支持私人对话</li>\n<li>\n支持群聊<ul>\n<li>支持 @ 机器人回复</li>\n<li>也支持命令（<code>/chatgpt</code>）触发，格式：<code>/chatgpt 你的聊天内容</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>[ WIP] 支持配置启动反向代理</li>\n<li>[WIP] 支持二次开发，快速接入企业现有应用</li>\n<li>[WIP] 支持 BingChat </li>\n</ul>\n<h3>预览</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu/raw/master/docs/assets/images/chatgpt.chat.group.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/go-zoox/chatgpt-for-chatbot-feishu/raw/master/docs/assets/images/chatgpt.chat.p2p.png\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1676766184,"replies":7,"id":917278},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":37437,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","stars":5191,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":533960,"username":"yunyuyuan","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yunyuyuan","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/368a3e37e2e947159548e7a306b9fcc0?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/368a3e37e2e947159548e7a306b9fcc0?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/368a3e37e2e947159548e7a306b9fcc0?s=73&d=retro","created":1613812748,"last_modified":1668773602},"last_reply_by":"ghjexxka","last_touched":1676763536,"title":"发现新大陆：年付 30 元 stardust 的 ipv6 only 小鸡","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/917335","created":1676785256,"deleted":0,"content":"提供商是 scaleway ，小鸡名字叫 stardust ，小鸡标配 1C1G ，硬盘 10G ，带宽 100M 不限流量。官网显示无库存，亲测可以用它提供的 cli 在命令行里开实例，当然前提是绑卡，需要支持外币的信用卡。\r\n\r\n我这里上海电信，ipv6 直连测速能跑满小鸡的 100M 带宽。搭了 v2ray ，ipv6 直连平均只有 10~20Mbps ，偶尔能到 50Mbps 。\r\n\r\n但是！套上 cloudflare tunnel 后，居然可以跑满带宽，我一直以为 cf tunnel 免费版限制了速度呢，下面是通过 cloudflare tunnel 连接小鸡的 v2ray 后的测试，油管 4k 是没问题的，就是不知道稳定性如何。\r\n\r\n年付 30 元搭梯子，想都不敢想！稍后写一篇小教程，需要配置 NAT64 。\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/7XZfWNP.png)\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.imgur.com/pCqSg8w.png)","content_rendered":"<p>提供商是 scaleway ，小鸡名字叫 stardust ，小鸡标配 1C1G ，硬盘 10G ，带宽 100M 不限流量。官网显示无库存，亲测可以用它提供的 cli 在命令行里开实例，当然前提是绑卡，需要支持外币的信用卡。</p>\n<p>我这里上海电信，ipv6 直连测速能跑满小鸡的 100M 带宽。搭了 v2ray ，ipv6 直连平均只有 10~20Mbps ，偶尔能到 50Mbps 。</p>\n<p>但是！套上 cloudflare tunnel 后，居然可以跑满带宽，我一直以为 cf tunnel 免费版限制了速度呢，下面是通过 cloudflare tunnel 连接小鸡的 v2ray 后的测试，油管 4k 是没问题的，就是不知道稳定性如何。</p>\n<p>年付 30 元搭梯子，想都不敢想！稍后写一篇小教程，需要配置 NAT64 。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7XZfWNP.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pCqSg8w.png\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1676785256,"replies":6,"id":917335},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":197451,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3702,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":308169,"username":"fingers","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fingers","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dd9a784d94e8acf9355cfbe94d44ef6e?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dd9a784d94e8acf9355cfbe94d44ef6e?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dd9a784d94e8acf9355cfbe94d44ef6e?s=73&d=retro","created":1523523848,"last_modified":1523523848},"last_reply_by":"testver","last_touched":1676786276,"title":"辉瑞的💊还有需要的吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/917331","created":1676784125,"deleted":0,"content":"之前某东买的，结果没用上，现在看来后面可能也用不上了","content_rendered":"之前某东买的，结果没用上，现在看来后面可能也用不上了","last_modified":1676784125,"replies":6,"id":917331},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_large.png?m=1670310953","name":"openai","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_normal.png?m=1670310953","title":"OpenAI","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/openai","topics":